QuestData.Title: The Might of the Warsong
QuestData.Description: <The officer is in a great deal of pain. It's clear that he's not long for this world.>$B$BThe Warsong. Surprise attack.$B$BHeaded into... the Burning Blade....$B$B<He takes a moment, before continuing.>$B$BThey took the... blueprints....$B$B<These are his last words.>
QuestData.RewardText: Commander $n. It's good to see you. We have much to discuss.$B$BThe situation in Nagrand is rapidly deteriorating. The Warsong clan is on the move.$B$BTo make matters worse, Grommash has named Garrosh their new warlord.$B$B<Thrall shakes his head sadly, but remains resolute.>
